  "summary": "What's Changed Add plural formatting to \"Group name is too long\" strings by @surfdude29 in #10769 [Chat] Fix overflowing chat names by @mozzius in #10780 Fix alignment of error screen by @ds-boyce in #10763 Use new listConvoRequests endpoint by @ds-boyce in #10755 Add Leave chat button to settings for chat owners by @ds-boyce in #10764 Show accept/reject fo…",
  "content": "<h2>What&#x27;s Changed</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Add plural formatting to &quot;Group name is too long&quot; strings by <a href=\"https://github.com/surfdude29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@surfdude29</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10769\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10769</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Fix overflowing chat names by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10780\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10780</a></li>\n<li>Fix alignment of error screen by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10763\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10763</a></li>\n<li>Use new listConvoRequests endpoint by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10755\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10755</a></li>\n<li>Add Leave chat button to settings for chat owners by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10764\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10764</a></li>\n<li>Show accept/reject footer for empty request convos by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10781\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10781</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Invite link dialog tweaks by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10750\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10750</a></li>\n<li>Block posting of invalid chat invites by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10757\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10757</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Fix footer logic by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10785\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10785</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Rename invite route to /chat/ by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10782\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10782</a></li>\n<li>Refactor photo embed analytics to post:photoEmbed:* namespace by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10784\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10784</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Centralize conversation report-subject resolution by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10754\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10754</a></li>\n<li>Add fade-in animation to chat footer/composer by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10786\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10786</a></li>\n<li>Open edit chat name dialog via tap by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10790\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10790</a></li>\n<li>Remove TODO for uninviting group chat members by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10789\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10789</a></li>\n<li>Only show Message option if chat member can be messaged by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10788\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10788</a></li>\n<li>Remove social proof from group invites by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10787\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10787</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Try and resolve loading bug once and for all by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10791\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10791</a></li>\n<li>Refactor age assurance flags and contexts by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10794\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10794</a></li>\n<li>Upgrade to pnpm 11.5.2 by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10793\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10793</a></li>\n<li>Hide last message in chat list if it&#x27;s blocked by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10800\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10800</a></li>\n<li>Mark string for translation and add context by <a href=\"https://github.com/surfdude29\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@surfdude29</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10805\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10805</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Gate group chats for under-18 users by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10548\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10548</a></li>\n<li>Fix fullscreen infinite render loop in video embeds by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10807\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10807</a></li>\n<li>Fix composer horizontal swipe triggering browser back/forward by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10812\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10812</a></li>\n<li>Catch NotAllowedError in web GIF player + lint modules/ by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10806\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10806</a></li>\n<li>Update handling of join link previews by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10798\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10798</a></li>\n<li>version number by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10815\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10815</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Filter out groups from badge counts when AA&#x27;d by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10816\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10816</a></li>\n<li>bskyweb: extract gallery media for SEO by <a href=\"https://github.com/blackmichael\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@blackmichael</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10813\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10813</a></li>\n<li>Fix text truncating in image menu on iOS by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10802\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10802</a></li>\n<li>Display toast after reacting emoji reaction limit by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10799\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10799</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Surface blocked members to top of group member list for owner by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10726\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10726</a></li>\n<li>Fix back button behavior on conversation settings screen by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10801\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10801</a></li>\n<li>Don&#x27;t suggest users who can&#x27;t be messaged/added by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10820\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10820</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Show invite link label in chat list preview by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10811\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10811</a></li>\n<li>Fix link to profile from chat invite embed by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10822\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10822</a></li>\n<li>Address chat design nits by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10823\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10823</a></li>\n<li>Add list of mutual chats to block dialog by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10727\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10727</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] add lil gap between chats on web by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10821\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10821</a></li>\n<li>Change Ignore to Reject for chat invites by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10825\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10825</a></li>\n<li>Fix image collapse in FF by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10826\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10826</a></li>\n<li>Hide domain if matches handle, new Standard Site icon treatment by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10767\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10767</a></li>\n<li>bskyweb: meta noindex tag for non-indexable pages by <a href=\"https://github.com/blackmichael\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@blackmichael</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10803\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10803</a></li>\n<li>Support dim theme on join request landing page by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10832\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10832</a></li>\n<li>Clear search term after adding chat member by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10831\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10831</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] revalidate join links on leave by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10833\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10833</a></li>\n<li>use opus 4.8 in github claude by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10837\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10837</a></li>\n<li>Remove leave-convo suppression, use real optimistic update by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10834\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10834</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Fix optimistic updates by using partial keys by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10838\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10838</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Some tweaks by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10840\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10840</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Sync convo agent with shadow cache by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10827\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10827</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Fix source of truth for group size limit by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10845\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10845</a></li>\n<li>Tweak spacing in invite link dialog by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10829\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10829</a></li>\n<li>Put display name and handle on one line in invite dialog by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10824\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10824</a></li>\n<li>Fix video preview collapse by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10847\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10847</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Delete <code>GroupChatGate</code> by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10846\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10846</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Fix duplicate messages when history fetch races firehose by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10839\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10839</a></li>\n<li>Enable Google Translate in post overflow menu by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10849\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10849</a></li>\n<li>New layout for expanded notification bundles by <a href=\"https://github.com/abenzer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@abenzer</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10664\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10664</a></li>\n<li>Restore on-device translation from overflow menu by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10850\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10850</a></li>\n<li>Invert group chat feature gate by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10851\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10851</a></li>\n<li>Add profile QR code for sharing and inviting friends by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10659\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10659</a></li>\n<li>Add indication of total number of images in ComposerReplyTo by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10836\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10836</a></li>\n<li>bskyweb: add video objects to jsonld SEO by <a href=\"https://github.com/blackmichael\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@blackmichael</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10814\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10814</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Reusable loading/unavailable states for chat invites by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10819\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10819</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Handle moderation lock override in group chats by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10835\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10835</a></li>\n<li>Add image to invite link NUX by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10852\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10852</a></li>\n<li>Peek preview for external link embeds by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10704\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10704</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] NUX by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10848\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10848</a></li>\n<li>[Chat] Power conversation settings screen via useConvoQuery by <a href=\"https://github.com/mozzius\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@mozzius</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10853\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10853</a></li>\n<li>Use add-only photo permission when saving QR codes by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10854\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10854</a></li>\n<li>Fix stale push notification replay after account switch by <a href=\"https://github.com/vineyardbovines\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@vineyardbovines</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10792\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10792</a></li>\n<li>Add new analytics events for group chats by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10830\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10830</a></li>\n<li>Let text wrap in invite dialog by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@estrattonbailey</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10855\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10855</a></li>\n<li>Log when a chat invite is posted or messaged by <a href=\"https://github.com/ds-boyce\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">@ds-boyce</a> in <a href=\"https://github.com/bluesky-social/social-app/pull/10858\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">#10858</a></li>\n<li>Release Prep 1.124.0 by <a href=\"https://github.com/estrattonbailey\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer